a.n: Goldenfighter Kickboxing Championship, Greece vs. China, Athens, Greece

p.d: GOLDEN FIGHTER Greece vs China is taking place on March 24th in Athens, Greece. It wil feature 10 Top Greek Fighters against 10 Chinese great fighters of WLF the best Chinese team. Between Greek fighters there are names as Giannis Boukis WKU,WLF world Champion, Giannis Sofokleous WAKO,WKU,ISKA,WPKA world champion, Fani Peloumpi WMC world champion and many other good fighters. Also there will be 1PRO Boxing world title fight WBO between Linardatou Christina (Dominic republic -Gre vs TBA). Fight card will present also title fights WLF, ISKA , WKU.
